      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a great start for the intro. for the next part of the essay, i need to address the counter-arguments so the paper looks well-rounded. how should i frame the arguments for meritocracy and the importance of individual property rights without making them sound weak or like they're just ignoring the history? i want to make sure i address them even if they don't work as well for my thesis.",
